{"tid":2207072,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打輕得太快?","createTime":"2020-09-18T02:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T05:33:49.000Z","uid":66945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ce818c4a93cd9e6162127f1c4e96c1d4ba5a9437","tid":2207072,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:47:03.000Z","msg":"男朋友佢冇做運動,食野又唔會話少過之前<br />\n我同佢一齊住, 所以我食咩佢都係食咩<br />\n我日日跑步都冇話輕左,但係佢冇做運動2個月體重都由130磅跌左落去120磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (高171cm)<br />\n同埋佢周不時都痾爛屎, 有d擔心佢腸胃係咪有問題<br />\n但係佢死都唔肯睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30c1907c5b3ba8dbc24698ce9454abc9e529324","tid":2207072,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"171cm 男人老狗 得120磅 咪就嚟死咁款"},{"pid":"188c4d52e2628bc583e36bdb5a9fd8d8e4028199","tid":2207072,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"排骨仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09bde5d0dc15ce24deb9369313c1f78898625efb","tid":2207072,"uid":344625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:57:45.000Z","msg":"做運動先重磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58a576aa4b720b43bc77da6fc8f180b8f1e9950","tid":2207072,"uid":44304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e30c1907c5b3ba8dbc24698ce9454abc9e529324","tid":2207072,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"171cm 男人老狗 得120磅 咪就嚟死咁款"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:58:00.000Z","msg":"冇做運動差唔多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b301e0316b56a0c8d755767c40f3af3329d56a38","tid":2207072,"uid":1082,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNkKXXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https